                        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$b">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                                 <p>This collection is housed in 9 boxes and organized into 5 series. The content of the collection consists of Houston Comet’s memorabilia documenting their four WNBA championship wins from years 1997 to 2000. In addition, general Houston Comet’s novelty items can be found in this collection dating from the year 1997 to 2003.</p>
                        </scopecontent>
            


